# ============================================================================
# Cost Optimization Tips
# ============================================================================

# For lower cost in dev environments:
# - Set enable_cis_level_2 = false
# - Set cloudtrail_log_retention = 30
# - Set guardduty_finding_frequency = "SIX_HOURS"
# - Set enable_inspector = false
# Estimated savings: ~$5-7/month

# For maximum security (production):
# - Enable all standards
# - Set longer retention periods
# - Enable all services
# Expected cost: ~$20-25/month